Class AbstractDiagramWizardContributor

    public abstract class AbstractDiagramWizardContributor
extends AbstractWizardContributor
implements IDiagramWizardContributor
    Convenience abstract class that provides an abstract implementation of IDiagramWizardContributor.

    Note to contributor implementors:
    This implementation is based on AbstractWizardContributor that supports fields and their getters/setters.
    This implementation also provides a default implementation of the #accept(MObject) method that deals with checking the scopes.
    By inheriting from this abstract class you only have to provide implementations for the two abstract methods:

    • AbstractWizardContributor.checkCanCreateIn(ModelElement)
    • AbstractWizardContributor.actionPerformed(ModelElement, String, String)
